Author: Alright#0419
Content:
Week 4 of STAKED will begin in ~1 hour. STAKED is an asset chain that incentivizes community members to test various aspects of Komodo's software. Users can be rewarded for finding bugs. If you're interested in learning the bleeding edge tech of Komodo, come visit us in the #private-staked channel. 
https://staked.cc/

Author: grewalsatinder#9653
Content:
Copy from Verus discord by @miketout 

We've just announced the latest planned update capabilities in a tweetstorm that calls out Vitalik Buterin, and Zcash's Zooko to ask for criticism of our new solution that solves two theoretical proof of stake issues by using an enhanced crypto-condition contract, activating on October 28th, along with Sapling support. There's a lot in the Tweet Storm, and the last tweet is a link to our community's @Oliver Westbrook 's article on how the new Stake Guard capability works. Again, this is a major breakthrough and not only a solution to fundamental proof of stake problems, but also leveraging enhancements to the Komodo crypto-conditions that will be fundamental to our PBaaS work. We plan to release the newest version a little later this week after full testing. Verus Coin's upcoming release is an advance worth sharing!
Enjoy!
https://twitter.com/VerusCoin/status/1049144468966785024
